        "text_KtTAAV": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>A lot of guitars online are posted exactly how they were found — dusty, untouched, vaguely described, and priced without much thought beyond profit.</p><p>That's not how Aeonic Frets works.</p><p>Every guitar that comes through here is fully cleaned, polished, set up, and played. Not because I have to — but because I love it. I want to know how it feels, how it rings, how it responds before I ever put it in someone else's hands. Sometimes I keep them. Sometimes I let one loose out of my personal collection.</p><p><strong>If it's listed here, it passed my standards first.</strong></p>",
            "text_style": "body"
